But I never played
against him, but he looks

00:37:04.400 --> 00:37:05.910
like a very talented player.

00:37:05.910 --> 00:37:09.560
I hope he can help us to
achieve our goals which we have.

00:37:09.560 --> 00:37:13.740
And I think he's a
very good player.

